  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Built from the taxidermic body of a basilisk, a <em>petrification cannon</em> functions as a <em>+2 greater striking double-barreled musket</em>. A <em>petrification cannon</em> can be activated to fire a beam of energy that transforms flesh into stone.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact (magical, transmutation)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A beam of coiling energy leaps from the <em>petrification cannon</em> at a target within 60 feet. The target must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:34] save against DC 34 with the effects of <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.znv4ECL7ZtuiagtA]{Petrify}</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> The initial raw materials must include the body of a basilisk.</p>"
